document_data.name: Geletha
document_data.mainbody:
'''Geletha''' was a female [[frost giant]] and part of a group of four of her kin who, along with around a hundred [[orc]]s, destroyed [[Clicking Heels]] in [[1370 DR]]. She was killed by the [[Companions of the Hall]] and [[Tred McKnuckles]] along with two of her comrades.
